HOMOGENEOUS ANISOTROPIC MODELS Our starting point is the family of Kantowski-Sachs metrics. We
choose these space-times because they combine both the non-trivial
curvature as well as the effects of anisotropy. We should note,
moreover, that we couldn't find any other non-pathological,
dynamical homogeneous and isotropic spacetime with the ghost
fields.

